23
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:28,000
This is where a player is going to take an item, already has the affixes that they want on it, but now they go through a process of upgrading those affixes, getting even higher values on them.

24
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:35,000
Masterworking really starts at level 100. Once you've already completed your build and found some of the best items, you're going to be able to test your build and get the best of the best of the best of the best.

25
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:52,000
